'''Hans Willem Capel''' (born 3 June 1936)<ref name=uva>{{cite web|author= |url=http://www.albumacademicum.uva.nl/cgi/b/bib/bib-idx?type=boolean;lang=en;searchtype=all;c=ap;q1=Capel;rgn1=entirerecord;op2=And;rgn2=entirerecord;op3=And;rgn3=entirerecord;op4=And;rgn4=entirerecord;date1=1576;date2=1992;date21=1636;date22=2016;date61=1634;date62=2016;cc=ap;view=reslist;sort=achternaam;fmt=long;page=reslist;start=4;size=1 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171226122343/http://www.albumacademicum.uva.nl/cgi/b/bib/bib-idx?type=boolean;lang=en;searchtype=all;c=ap;q1=Capel;rgn1=entirerecord;op2=And;rgn2=entirerecord;op3=And;rgn3=entirerecord;op4=And;rgn4=entirerecord;date1=1576;date2=1992;date21=1636;date22=2016;date61=1634;date62=2016;cc=ap;view=reslist;sort=achternaam;fmt=long;page=reslist;start=4;size=1 |title=Prof. dr. H.W. Capel, 1936 - |publisher=University of Amsterdam |date= |archive-date=26 December 2017}}</ref> is a Dutch theoretical physicist. He was a professor of theoretical physics at the [[University of Amsterdam]] between 1983 and 1998.<ref name=uva/>
Capel was born in Sceaux, France. He obtained his PhD in mathematics and physics at [[Leiden University]] in 1965 with a dissertation titled: "The hole-equivalence principle, the Van Vleck relation and the application to the theory of d-ions in Ligand fields".<ref name=uva/> Capel subsequently was a lector of theoretical physics at same the university in 1970, and served as professor between 1979 and 1983.<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://hoogleraren.leidenuniv.nl/id/411 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171227122153/http://hoogleraren.leidenuniv.nl/id/411 |title=Hans Willem Capel |publisher=Leiden University |date= |archive-date=27 December 2017}}</ref>
Capel was elected a member of the [[Royal Netherlands Academy of Arts and Sciences]] in 1990.<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=https://knaw.nl/en/members/members/3976 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171226122234/https://knaw.nl/en/members/members/3976 |title=Hans Capel |publisher=Royal Netherlands Academy of Arts and Sciences |date= |archive-date=26 December 2017}}</ref>
