{{Infobox Magazine|
  title          = Info Exame |
  company        = [[Editora Abril]] |
  editors        = Airton Lopes, Maurício Moraes, Maria Isabel Moreira |
  frequency      = Monthly |
  circulation    = nearly 200,000 |
  category       = Technology magazine |
  country        = [[Brazil]] |
